    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_9_46761-46773",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "46761-46773",
      "markText": "“惟其痛苦，才有欢乐。”",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=46761&rangeEnd=46773",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=46761&rangeEnd=46773"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_9_9613-9707",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9613-9707",
      "markText": "毫无疑问，心灵需要时间来适应痛苦。它那么需要快乐，所以没有快乐的时候，只能自己来制造。现实太残酷时，它便回到过去的生活中去。昔日快乐的时光不会一下子抹掉，即使欢愉不再，其光辉也会久久留存。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9613&rangeEnd=9707",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9613&rangeEnd=9707"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_6_2434-2521",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2434-2521",
      "markText": "没有伟大的品格，就没有伟大的人，同样也没有伟大的艺术家、伟大的行动者；而只有一些为群氓而立的腹中空空的偶像，时间会将它们统统摧毁。成败无关紧要，重要的是伟大，而不是显得伟大。",
      "totalCount": 510,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2434&rangeEnd=2521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2434&rangeEnd=2521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_5_429-459",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "429-459",
      "markText": "“打开窗子吧！让自由的空气重新进来！让我们呼吸英雄的气息。”",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=429&rangeEnd=459",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=429&rangeEnd=459"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_6_636-893",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "636-893",
      "markText": "我愿证明，谁若行为高尚、善良， 必同样能承受苦难。 ——贝多芬",
      "totalCount": 406,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=893",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=636&rangeEnd=893"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_5_6461-6528",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6461-6528",
      "markText": "“生活是严酷的，对那些不安于平庸的人说来，生活就是一场无休止的搏斗，而且往往是无荣誉无幸福可言的、在孤独中默默进行的一场可悲的搏斗。”",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6461&rangeEnd=6528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6461&rangeEnd=6528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_10_2715-2761",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2715-2761",
      "markText": "谁要是不兼爱欢乐和痛苦，便是两者都不爱。谁懂得品尝它们，便能体会活着的价值和离开人生的甜蜜。",
      "totalCount": 357,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2715&rangeEnd=2761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2715&rangeEnd=2761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_13_25227-25262",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "25227-25262",
      "markText": "我发现，世界上有一种不朽的东西，有一种爱，要永远幸福就必须为他人活着。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=25227&rangeEnd=25262",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=25227&rangeEnd=25262"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_8_402-514",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "402-514",
      "markText": "善事应尽力而为， 爱自由甚于一切， 即使为了帝王的宝座， 也绝不出卖真理。",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_6_2847-2869",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2847-2869",
      "markText": "生活从来不曾像在患难中那样伟大、丰盈和幸福。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2847&rangeEnd=2869",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2847&rangeEnd=2869"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_10_2158-2199",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2158-2199",
      "markText": "信仰往往只是生活中缺乏信心的表现，对将来、对自己缺乏信心、失去勇气和欢乐的表现！…",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2158&rangeEnd=2199",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2158&rangeEnd=2199"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_12_1203-1295",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1203-1295",
      "markText": "我并不认为一般人都能生活在高山之巅。但不妨一年一度登高礼拜。他们可以在那儿更新肺部的气息和脉管中的血液。在高处，他们会感到更加接近永恒。待回到人生的平原，他们将满怀勇气面对日常的搏斗。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1203&rangeEnd=1295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1203&rangeEnd=1295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_5_1466-1561",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1466-1561",
      "markText": "但他们肯定具有一种内在的强大生命力，使他们在任何逆境中都不放弃奋斗；他们饱经忧患，历尽艰辛，却始终牢牢把握着自己的命运，以顽强的意志去战胜一切困难，竭尽努力使自己成为无愧于“人”的称号的人。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1466&rangeEnd=1561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1466&rangeEnd=1561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_7_2596-2612",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2596-2612",
      "markText": "是他，教给了我们如何生，如何死。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2596&rangeEnd=2612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2596&rangeEnd=2612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_9_10507-10561",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10507-10561",
      "markText": "他的挚友辛德勒很有把握地说，“他一生洁身自爱，从未有过越轨的行为。”这样的人注定要上爱情的当，成为其牺牲品。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10507&rangeEnd=10561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10507&rangeEnd=10561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_9_12435-12483",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12435-12483",
      "markText": "不，我不能忍受下去。我要扼住命运的咽喉，它永远不能使我完全屈服。啊，如果能活上千百次那就太好了！",
      "totalCount": 231,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12435&rangeEnd=12483",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12435&rangeEnd=12483"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_5_11086-11097",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11086-11097",
      "markText": "“人啊！靠你自己吧！”",
      "totalCount": 228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11086&rangeEnd=11097",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11086&rangeEnd=11097"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303630_3_946-1022",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "946-1022",
      "markText": "较之常人，社会和自然并未给予伟人们更多惠顾，生活对他们而言往往是一场无休止的搏斗。凭着坚强的毅力，他们勇于承受磨难，勇于挑战困难，终于攀登上生命的巅峰。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303630&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=946&rangeEnd=1022",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74032d80716395ce740fbf4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=946&rangeEnd=1022"
    },
    {
